4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp that allows students to become proficient in JavaScript and Python, two highly sought-after programming languages. The program lasts for 16+2 weeks, with three classes held weekly. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. No previous coding skills or advanced math are required. The program focuses on web development, algorithm scripting, app building using front-end libraries, and API utilization. Students will also develop and present their own project, gaining hands-on experience. The bootcamp is available in both English and Spanish, with live classes taught in the language of the campus. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer. stop